The homeowners association met again on Thursday to reconsider the playhouse proposal and decided to relent. 

Stonegate HOA released the following statement: 'Today, we are happy to share that we have reached a positive resolution to ensure Ella's playhouse will be constructed.

'Our board met with JE Dunn Construction and Make a Wish to gather additional information, and while we still have a few details and timelines to work out, we collectively reached the conclusion that Ella will get her wish.

'We couldn't be more pleased to see that happen.'  

